    <description>Interaction Log Distribution

Once an interaction log has a discussion type and has its status set to &#39;Final&#39;, this flow builds a distribution list baseed on the profile of the user to enter the IL and the discussion type. 

User CMDT and public groups to bring together userss into this distribution list.</description>
    <environments>Default</environments>
    <formulas>
        <description>Returns the name of a public group based on the Discussion Type of the triggering Interaction Log.</description>
        <name>f_DiscussionTypeToPublicGroupMapping</name>
        <dataType>String</dataType>
        <expression>IF(TEXT({!$Record.leaseworks__Discussion_Type__c}) = &#39;Credit Update&#39;, &#39;Credit_Update&#39;,
IF(TEXT({!$Record.leaseworks__Discussion_Type__c}) = &#39;General&#39;, &#39;General&#39;,
IF(TEXT({!$Record.leaseworks__Discussion_Type__c}) = &#39;Technical&#39;, &#39;Tech_Kick_Off&#39;,
IF(TEXT({!$Record.leaseworks__Discussion_Type__c}) = &#39;Marketing Intel&#39;, &#39;Market_Intel&#39;,
IF(TEXT({!$Record.leaseworks__Discussion_Type__c}) = &#39;RFP&#39;, &#39;RFP&#39;,
IF(TEXT({!$Record.leaseworks__Discussion_Type__c}) = &#39;PDP&#39;, &#39;PDP&#39;,
IF(TEXT({!$Record.leaseworks__Discussion_Type__c}) = &#39;Trading&#39;, &#39;Trading&#39;,
IF(TEXT({!$Record.leaseworks__Discussion_Type__c}) = &#39;General - Marketing Team&#39;, &#39;pro_General_Marketing_Team&#39;,
&#39;Other&#39;
))))))))</expression>
    </formulas>
    <formulas>
        <description>Returns the name of a public group to be included in distribution list based on the Profile of the user to create the Interaction Log</description>
        <name>f_ProfileToPublicGroupMapping</name>
        <dataType>String</dataType>
        <expression>IF({!$Record.CreatedBy.Profile.Name} = &#39;Carlyle Commercial&#39;, &#39;Market_Intel&#39;, Null)</expression>
    </formulas>
    <interviewLabel>Prodigy - IL - Email Distribution List Once IL Final {!$Flow.CurrentDateTime}</interviewLabel>
    <label>Prodigy - IL - Email Distribution List Once IL Final</label>
